### CopyAI API

To use the AI generation feature, you need a Hugging Face token.

1. Get a token from https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens
2. Create a `.env.local` file in the project root with:

```
HF_TOKEN=your_hugging_face_token_here
```

**Production (e.g. Railway/Vercel):** Set `VITE_API_URL` to your deployed API origin so the frontend calls the right host (e.g. `VITE_API_URL=https://web-production-579dd.up.railway.app`). Leave unset locally to use the Vite proxy to localhost:3001.
